---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — The Askesis Project" currentPage="/about">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section>
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 72px;">
      <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #a35c41; margin-bottom: 30px;">About</div>
      <h1 style="font-size: 64px; line-height: 1.06; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.018em; margin: 0; max-width: 880px; text-wrap: balance;">It started as a document of one person's midlife transformation.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY + PORTRAIT -->
  <section>
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-bottom: 96px;">
      <div class="story-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px; gap: 64px; align-items: start;">
        <div style="max-width: 620px;">
          <p style="font-size: 21px; line-height: 1.6; color: #2a2620; margin: 0 0 26px;">For most of my life I treated discipline as something other people had — a fixed trait, a gift withheld. Then, somewhere past forty, the question stopped being <em>why am I like this</em> and became <em>what would it take to change.</em></p>
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: #4a443c; margin: 0 0 22px;">The answer turned out to be unglamorous: a body kept in motion, attention trained like a muscle, and the same small acts repeated until they became character. Not a transformation that arrives, but one you assemble, one ordinary morning at a time.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: #4a443c; margin: 0 0 22px;">The Askesis Project is the open notebook of that work. Here you'll find the tools I used and the experiences I had while reshaping my life with intention — including the parts that didn't work, which were most of them, for a while.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: #4a443c; margin: 0;">I write this in public because the practice is steadier when it's witnessed, and because somewhere out there is the version of me from five years ago, looking for a place to start.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="border: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.14); aspect-ratio: 4/5; overflow: hidden;">
            <img src="/founder.jpg" alt="The founder of The Askesis Project" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" />
          </div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #8a8175; margin-top: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Writer, coach, and perpetual beginner. Based wherever the practice travels.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE SYMBOL -->
  <section style="background: #1a1714; color: #ece5d6;">
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 96px;">
      <div class="symbol-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: start;">
        <div>
          <img src="/enso.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; object-fit: contain; filter: invert(1); opacity: 0.92;" />
        </div>
        <div style="max-width: 720px;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #c98a6e; margin-bottom: 24px;">The symbol</div>
          <p style="font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 300; margin: 0 0 26px; text-wrap: pretty;">The <em>ensō</em> is drawn in a single uninterrupted breath. It is never perfect, and that is the point — it shows the moment exactly as it was, hand and mind and circumstance, with nothing hidden.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: #b3aa9b; margin: 0;">Inside it sits the <em>alpha</em> — the beginning, the first letter, the place you return to each day. Practice and beginning, held in one mark.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THIS IS / ISN'T -->
  <section>
    <div class="wrapper" style="padding-top: 96px; padding-bottom: 96px;">
      <div class="is-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: rgba(26,23,20,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(26,23,20,0.12);">
        <div style="background: #f3efe6; padding: 46px 40px;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6f675b; margin-bottom: 28px;">What this is</div>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px;"><span style="color: #a35c41;">→&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Applied effort toward meaningful change.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px;"><span style="color: #a35c41;">→&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>A practice you build daily, with intention.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px;"><span style="color: #a35c41;">→&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>A document of real transformation — mess included.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px;"><span style="color: #a35c41;">→&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Movement, mind, and character treated as one work.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #efe9dd; padding: 46px 40px;">
          <div style="font-family: 'Spline Sans Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6f675b; margin-bottom: 28px;">What it isn't</div>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px; color: #6f675b;"><span style="color: #b0a698;">—&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Asceticism, or discipline disguised as denial.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px; color: #6f675b;"><span style="color: #b0a698;">—&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>A 30-day challenge or a productivity system.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px; color: #6f675b;"><span style="color: #b0a698;">—&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Optimization for its own restless sake.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; padding-left: 26px; text-indent: -26px; color: #6f675b;"><span style="color: #b0a698;">—&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>A finished person telling you how it's done.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  h1 { font-size: 46px !important; }
  .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  .symbol-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  .is-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  h1 { font-size: 36px !important; }
}
</style>
